  "text": "Wu et al. [CITATION_1] propose an approach to automatically link code changes with corresponding bug reports together. Our work is complementary to theirs. We recover root causes from such code changes that correspond to fixes to issues mentioned in bug reports, and our results may potentially be used to improve the quality of their results.",
